    <briefdescription>
<para>Control block for a CMSIS-RTOSv2 thread. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Application can use manual user-defined allocation for RTOS objects by supplying a pointer to thread control block. Control block is initiazed within <computeroutput>osThreadNew()</computeroutput>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
